  "texts": [
    "This can involve removing irrelevant content, such as headers, footers, and non-text elements, as well as handling special characters and formatting issues.",
    "Text Segmentation and Embedding GenerationThe extracted text from the text files undergoes segmentation into smaller units, enhancing the efficiency of subsequent processing and analysis.",
    "This segmentation divides the text into manageable chunks, enabling the system to focus on specific aspects of the information.",
    "Following segmentation, the system generates embeddings for the segmented text.",
    "Embeddings are numerical representations of text that capture the semantic meaning of the information."
